nodes.text: Aneese Palladane was the older prepubescent daughter of the covert Jedi Knight Gorlan Palladane and Roah Palladane in the Outer Rim world of Chelloa during the Republic Dark Age. She and her family lived in the mining colony of Jenith.

In 1032 BBY, her parents sheltered the female Jedi Knight Kerra Holt, the last surviving member of the ill-fated Operation Influx. Following the arrest of her father by Sith Lord Daiman, Daiman's forces plundered and murdered the inhabitants of Jenith. During the crackdown, the Palladane home was invaded by a pair of Sith troopers. However, the Palladanes were rescued by Holt, who slew the two home invaders.
